results.title: Stained Birch Wood Coasters, Birch Bark Coasters, Inspirational Calligraphy Quotes, Dream Love Laugh Smile, 4" Round [Pack of 4]
results.description:
This listing is for approximately 4" round and 1/2" thick oil-stained birchwood coasters with each one having an inspirational word written in cursive on them. The birch wood was allowed to air dry to an acceptable moisture content before being sanded smooth, oiled with linseed oil, stained with a premium oil stain, sealed with shellac and water polyurethane then finished off with a light coat of beeswax. 

The mugs shown range from 8oz, 12oz, and 16oz. These coasters are suitable for all mug sizes.  

CARE: They may be gently wiped down with soapy water. Do not submerge under water or drench them. Although sealed, the coasters will still react to extremely humid/damp environments causing them to warp and shortening their lifespan. If they look a little worn after a while using an oil-based furniture polish will help them look rejuvenated.
